Rune memiliki kemampuan: 
 - secara otomatis menyimpan semua data di cloud; 
 - langsung mengaksesnya di perangkat lain; 
 - simpan tidak hanya catatan teks, tetapi juga file dalam format apa pun; 

 Secara default, aplikasi bekerja tanpa sinkronisasi dan menyimpan semua data di perangkat. 
 `` 
 Setelah Anda mengaktifkan rune ini, semua data yang dibuat sebelumnya dan baru akan secara otomatis disinkronkan ke penyimpanan cloud setelah koneksi internet tersedia. 
 ``

The rune gives you the ability to use the application to fill in input fields with existing notes in almost **any application**. 

 Once activated, when you place focus in an input field, the app will display a floating panel with actions that allow you to control the content of the input field. 

 #### Behavior features: 
 - the panel can be dragged anywhere on the screen; 
 - the panel can be automatically modified depending on the possibility of using certain actions; 
 - the panel can be automatically hidden if the field loses focus; 
 - the panel can be manually hidden (via action in the toolbar) until forced to be called again; 
 - if the panel is not displayed, it can be explicitly called from the notification panel (by clicking on the corresponding notification) or by double-tapping on any input field; 

 #### Technical limitations: 
 - the panel uses accessibility service and requires its activation in the system settings; 
 - the panel uses a floating window to display on top of other applications and requires the corresponding permission in the system settings; 
 - in some applications the automatic behavior of the panel is not possible, so it can be used with restrictions and explicit invocation; 

 #### Notice: 
 If the rune stops working after a while please read [this article](%s) how to keep the app running on your device. Or contact me by email, maybe you found some issue:)

Saat rune ini diaktifkan, untuk **http link** yang disimpan, aplikasi akan mencoba memuat pratinjaunya dalam mode tampilan catatan. 

 Dalam melakukannya: 
 - gambar pratinjau bisa dibuka di jendela terpisah dan diperbesar; 
 - Kalau tautannya adalah video, maka dapat diputar dengan aplikasi lho;

In addition to cloud synchronization, you can manually save backups of your data and restore them later. 

 Unlike cloud synchronization, this approach allows: 
 - take a snapshot of all data at the current moment of time; 
 - manage the entire backup and recovery process by yourself; 
 - restore the entire data based on the previously saved data snapshot; 

 ``` 
 Restoring from a file is done in a soft mode. That is, the existing data is not deleted, but only supplemented with new data. 
 ```
